review-unclosed-style-tag,"Unclosed <style> tag. The preprocessStyleTags regex requires a closing </style> to match; if absent, the raw CSS body would bypass postcss sanitization without the uponSanitizeElement backstop.",malicious,at-rule,style-src,code review P1 finding — preprocessStyleTags regex bypass + backstop,<style>@import url(https://attacker.example/evil.css)</style>,
